<h2 id="Syntax">Syntax</h2>
<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/CSS_values_syntax#syntax-box" title="border-box | padding-box | content-box">&lt;box&gt;</a><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#Hash_mark_(.23)" title="Hash mark multiplier: the previous entity may appear 0, 1 or several times, each occurence being separated from the previous one by a comma">#</a></code></pre>
<pre>background-origin: border-box
background-origin: padding-box
background-origin: content-box

background-origin: inherit
</pre>
<h3 id="Values">Values</h3>
<dl><dt>
  <code>border-box</code></dt>
 <dd>
  The background extends to the outside edge of the border (but underneath the border in z-ordering).</dd>
 <dt>
  <code>padding-box</code></dt>
 <dd>
  No background is drawn below the border (background extends to the outside edge of the padding).</dd>
 <dt>
  <code>content-box</code></dt>
 <dd>
  The background is painted within (clipped to) the content box.</dd>
</dl>